title: Chatty
description: Created an AI technical interview plateform to help students prepare for coding and finance interviews through a conversational AI. Supports over 1000+ questions and used by students at UVA and UMD!

title: Moji
description: Moji utilizes HumeAI to match the emotional sentiment of a live meeting to over 80+ emojis, giving a real time heads up display to the organizer of the meeting. This project was created at the 2024 Berkeley Hackathon!

title: Find My Hospital
description: This product was made to combat the difficulty to find hospital beds post-pandemic. Utilizing API's like GeoPy and predictive modeling, I was able to create an interactive database that allows users to find the closest bed to their location.
